{"tid":716860,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"世盃唯一！迪基亞撲救捧蛋","createTime":"2018-06-25T15:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T04:00:56.000Z","uid":333,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"bf85add506a4bcc38334efa7dc0c40d12b41da53","tid":716860,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T15:28:11.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=6u3WKRALOrPV2yHo7Ghbi7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=3defcdc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】國際足協最近公佈世界盃撲救排行榜，墨西哥門將奧祖亞排第1，第2是丹麥的卡斯柏舒米高，至於西班牙的迪基亞竟然沒有錄得任何成功撲救。<br />\n<br />\n根據國際足協官方網站提供的統計數據，西班牙門將迪基亞（David de Gea）是33位至今出戰過今屆世界盃的門將當中，唯一一位沒有作出過任何成功撲救的門將。<br />\n<br />\n迪基亞在雙「牙」戰中，於上半場尾段犯下大錯，牛油手誤把基斯坦奴朗拿度射球拍入網，西班牙跟葡萄牙最終踢成3:3平手，失掉3球；不過，備受批評的他之後對伊朗的比賽就力保不失，狂牛兵團最終以1:0贏波。<br />\n<br />\n排行榜第1的是墨西哥門將奧祖亞，他以14球撲救領先，丹麥的卡斯柏舒米高以10球緊隨其後，哥斯達黎加的基羅拿華斯、澳洲的馬菲賴恩、冰島的賀度臣就齊齊以9球排第3。<br />\n<br />\n至於烏拉圭的梅斯利拿（6球）、克羅地亞的蘇巴錫（5球）就錄得100%的救球率。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙VS摩洛哥<br />\nNow618台26/06 01:15直播"},{"pid":"d9001a3ce0de971ab6a8130699b6400d410bdfa3","tid":716860,"uid":30751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18016f1ea475922a678e4aaffa46a82e7a114aa4","tid":716860,"uid":4160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:19:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9531828b651f294f30f4a0c0d9b15cad1d916a3b","tid":716860,"uid":52006,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:20:26.000Z","msg":"黃大仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2035a03e9731dd0bb0b6dd13c16e83b7ff49fb4","tid":716860,"uid":35365,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16